text: Ayu Sita Widyastuti Nugraha (born June 9, 1989, Jakarta, Indonesia) is an Indonesian pop singer, hip hop dancer, actress, and host. ==Cinematography== ===Movies=== * Me vs High Heels (2005) * Bukan Bintang Biasa (2007) * Langit Biru (2011) * What They Don't Talk About When They Talk About Love (2013) ==TV series== * Sinetron Ramadhan: Zahra (2008) * Salon Cimey (2014) * Dancing with the Stars Indonesian (2015) * The East (2015) * Breakout (2015) with Boy William ==FTV== * Bekisar Merah * Spagheti * Kutu,kan ==Discography== ===with BBB=== * 2006 - Bukan Bintang Biasa ===Collaborations=== * 2009 - OST.
